      "text": "{user}君を随分待たせちゃったけど\nこれでやっと、あの時の約束が果たせるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ I've made you wait for quite a while‚\nbut now we can finally keep our words we made back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2000000953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.166666762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんとライブの計画を立てて……\n二人でこっそり歌とダンスを練習して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Planning the live performance with Mana-chan…\nSecretly practicing singing and dancing together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2000000953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.3666663805
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "この日のために新しい衣装を作って……\n内緒で会場を準備して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Designing new outfits for this day…\nPreparing the venue in secret…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7999997138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "あの時伝えられなかった感謝の気持ちを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Expressing the gratitude we couldn't convey back then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2999997138,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9633.3351096,
          "startTime": 30.9333348234
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12490.460153500002,
          "startTime": 33.7904598673
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13100.0002862,
          "startTime": 34.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.5333330471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんと二人で重ねた想いを\n今日、私達が届けるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The feelings we shared‚ Mana-chan and I‚\nwe'll deliver them today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7666663805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.9333348234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　{user}君からだわ\n……もしもし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? A call from you‚ {user}?\nHello?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし、遙子さんですか？\n事務所にあった招待状を見て会場に来たんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ is this Haruko-san?\nI came to the venue after seeing the invitation at the office…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1666693051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "客席には俺達の他に誰もいないんですが\n場所はここで合ってますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there's no one else in the audience except us.\nAm I at the right place?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3000026385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.7333359718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "そこで合ってるわよ\nすぐに行くから、席に座って待っててくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're at the right place.\nI'll be there soon‚ please sit and wait?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7000026385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、橋本さんと待ってます\n……でも、これから何が始まるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood‚ I'll wait with Hashimoto-san.\n…But what's about to start?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8000026385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.2666693051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "すぐに分かるわ。それじゃ、また後でね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You'll find out soon enough. See you later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2666693051,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5333.330694899999,
          "startTime": 69.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "時間が経って形も変わったけど……\n二人の約束、叶えようね、麻奈ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Though time has passed and things have changed…\nLet's fulfill the promise between the two of us‚ Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.566670831,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8333430926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さん、さとみちゃん、{user}君）\n（今の私達がいるのはみんなのおかげよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Saegusa-san‚ Satomi-chan‚ {user}）\n（We're all here now thanks to everyone.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.0666764259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.0333415667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "（だから心を込めて歌うわ）\n（昔、麻奈ちゃんが教えてくれたように……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So let's sing with all our hearts.）\n（Just like Mana-chan taught us back then…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5000082333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.0000133196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなに私達の想いが届くように！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So our feelings can reach everyone!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0000133196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage",
      "startTime": 100.3666799862
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage",
      "startTime": 100.3666799862
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage",
      "startTime": 100.6000102678
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "驚いたな……\n俺達に秘密でこんなライブを計画していたなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surprising…\nPlanning such a live performance in secret…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7000051815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなが見ていてくれるから私達は頑張れる）\n（みんなの支えがあるから私達は輝ける）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Because everyone is watching‚ we can do our best.）\n（Because everyone supports us‚ we can shine.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2666703223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "（私達が笑顔で歌えるのはみんなのおかげよ）\n（私達を輝かせてくれてありがとう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We can sing with smiles because of everyone.）\n（Thank you for making us shine.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0000021297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "（これからも私はみんなと前に進みたい）\n（どこまでも遠くへ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（From now on‚ I want to move forward with everyone.）\n（To wherever‚ to the farthest reaches…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2999990779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんのことは昔から知ってるけど\n見違えるくらいに成長したな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've known you‚ Haruko-san‚ since long ago‚ but…\nYou've grown so much‚ it's like seeing a different person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8000051814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "辛い時も腐らず、地道に努力を積み重ねた成果だ\n誰よりも頑張ってきた遙子さんは、とても輝いているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's the result of your unwavering efforts‚ even in tough times.\nHaruko-san‚ who has worked harder than anyone else‚ is truly shining.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6666779516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wing",
      "startTime": 153.3333619115
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wing",
      "startTime": 153.3333619115
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wing",
      "startTime": 158.7666769344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "（……麻奈ちゃん。あなたの想いが詰まった曲を）\n（あなたの後輩達が心を込めて歌うわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana-chan‚ the song filled with your hearts…）\n（Your juniors will sing it with all their hearts.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.7666769344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
